| Phase | Step | Description | Depends On |
|-------|------|-------------|------------|
| 1 | Step 1 | Schema changes | None |
| 1 | Step 2 | Type system updates | None |
| 2 | Step 3 | Provenance validation (verify no change needed) | Step 2 |
| 2 | Step 4 | Entity upsert updates | Step 1, Step 2 |
| 2 | Step 5 | Persist extraction updates | Step 4 |
